    <sec id="SEC2-2">
      <title>The AptaBlocks algorithm</title>
      <p>We describe our method in more details in the following. First, weoutline our biophysics based model to compute the probabilities that characterize the structural properties mentioned above. Then, we elucidate the heat-bath algorithm, a Monte Carlo method closely related to the classical (Metropolis-based) simulated annealing, that AptaBlocks uses to optimize these probabilities as well as the melting temperature, subject to possible additional constraints the user might impose on <italic>B</italic> and <inline-formula><tex-math id="M23">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
